text:
Wow... this page also has Luca in it~...!
So cool...

Her expressions and poses are truly remarkable.
I bet she finished the photoshoot in an instant.

I always feel unsure of what to do...
and end up panicking...

I wonder how Luca-chan handles herself
during photoshoots...

...It's better to be prepared.
To some extent...

Preparation, huh...
Like simulating before the shoot...?

Yeah, that's right...!
Let's think about it together, Haruki-chan...!
